Text: Contract Assignments and Agency Terminations Cc Im not sure if you are the correct person to receive this message We have been checking with all the applicable pipelines to make sure the transport and storage capacity is back in BUNYs name as of April All of the pipelines appear to be on board but Texas Gas and TETCO specifically seem to be expecting some correspondence from BUNY to this effect We want to make sure all of this goes smoothly next week so could you guys let us know where this stands in your shop Thanks Kate Kate Fraser Manager Commodities Trading Enron North America Fax

BUG OA Cc In late June David Oliver gave me a final OA adjustment for the BUG deal The figure he gave me was We have not run this through the PL yet because there are other outstanding issues that we expect to net out against this loss Could you provide a breakdown of this figure Colleen Sullivan has agreed to help the desk with final settlement of the BUG deal and we want to make sure that this OA figure does not include some other issues we are working on Please provide this breakdown to both Colleen and myself Thanks Kate
